OL,5,GLast week we noted the temporary
OL,6,Gincrease in advertising on the three
OL,7,Gmain commercial channels.
OL,9,FITV, Channel 4 and Channel 5 all lost
OL,10,Fsome advertising time following the
OL,11,Fdeath of HM The Queen and during the
OL,12,Fperiod of mourning.
OL,14,FWith Ofcom's approval they can now make
OL,15,Fup some of the "lost minutes" by
OL,16,Frunning more adverts than normal.
OL,18,FThe big rule is that they still cannot
OL,19,Fhave more than 12 minutes in a clock
OL,20,Fhour.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?
OL,22,                                   G1/6
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
