OL,5,FSo does this offer us a taste of what
OL,6,Fthings may be like if Ofcom allows a
OL,7,Fpermanent increase in the amount of
OL,8,Fadvertising on the three main
OL,9,Fcommercial PSBs?
OL,11,FWe looked carefully at advertising
OL,12,Fbetween 5pm and 12am on ITV between
OL,13,FFriday and Sunday.
OL,15,FThere was 12 minutes of advertising in
OL,16,Fthe 5pm, 7pm, 8pm, 9pm and 11pm hours.
OL,18,FThe 6pm hour contained two breaks  one
OL,19,Fof 4 minutes between the regional and
OL,20,Fnational news and one of 3 minutes 30
OL,21,Fseconds at approximately 6.45pm.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?
OL,22,                                   G2/6
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
