OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1667777620
OL,5,FIf a full 12 minutes were to be allowed
OL,6,Fin each hour, the likelihood is that 2
OL,7,Fmore breaks would be included totalling
OL,8,F4 minutes and 30 seconds.
OL,10,FIn the 10pm hour, there was 8 minutes
OL,11,Fof advertising  4 minutes before News
OL,12,Fat Ten and 4 minutes after the regional
OL,13,Fnews. Again 4 minutes would need to be
OL,14,Ffound to "max out" each hour.
OL,16,FIt should be noted that internal breaks
OL,17,Fcan normally only include 3 minutes 30
OL,18,Fof ads but there is no cap on the
OL,19,Famount during breaks between
OL,20,Fprogrammes.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?
OL,22,                                   G3/6
