OL,5,FThere was one "trail break" at around
OL,6,F5.55pm which could have been extended
OL,7,Fand replaced by a 3 minute 30 seconds
OL,8,Fad break.
OL,10,FAfter 6pm, only the 8pm hour didn't
OL,11,Finclude a full 12 minutes of ads  it
OL,12,Fonly included 10 minutes and 30 seconds
OL,13,Fworth.
OL,15,FBetween 5pm and 12am there was almost
OL,16,Fas much advertising as would be
OL,17,Fallowable after any potential increase.
OL,19,FThe 6pm hour fell slightly short by 30
OL,20,Fseconds.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?
