OL,5,FIt's certainly interesting to get a
OL,6,Fsense of what things could potentially
OL,7,Fbe like in a few months time.
OL,9,FSaturday and Sunday evenings on ITV
OL,10,Fwould hardly be any different 
OL,11,Falthough a little reconfiguration could
OL,12,Fbe needed.
OL,14,FThere is also the question of whether
OL,15,Fprogramme durations might need to be
OL,16,Ftweaked to ensure the schedule runs to
OL,17,Ftime and that there is room for
OL,18,Fpromotions  some promo time has been
OL,19,Fsacrificed to allow for the temporary
OL,20,Fincrease in adverts.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?
OL,22,                                   G5/6
